==English==
===Etymology===
AS. æftan behind; originally superlative of &ldquo;of&rdquo;, off.  See [[After]].

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /æft/

===Adverb===
'''aft'''
# {{nautical}} At or towards the [[stern]] of a [[vessel]] (with the frame of reference within the vessel).

